ivardefs.name: documentation
ivardefs.desc: Documentation about the system's messaging capabilities for this endpoint not otherwise documented by the capability statement.  For example, the process for becoming an authorized messaging exchange partner.

ivardefs.name: endpoint_
ivardefs.desc: An endpoint (network accessible address) to which messages and/or replies are to be sent.

ivardefs.name: reliableCache
ivardefs.desc: Length if the receiver's reliable messaging cache in minutes (if a receiver) or how long the cache length on the receiver should be (if a sender).

ivardefs.name: supportedMessage_
ivardefs.desc: References to message definitions for messages this system can send or receive.

properties.desc: A description of the messaging capabilities of the solution.
